{"tid":195943,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 新手，我問你答","createTime":"2017-04-11T03:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T09:37:36.000Z","uid":64615,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2398c6f2c609224501d8747194932fb249b567fe","tid":195943,"uid":64615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:13:22.000Z","msg":"新入手ps4 <br />\n睇緊有咩game 好入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前psp 玩過隻賽車game 好真實，但唔記得咩名想搵番<br />\n隻賽車game 嘅真實主要係講部車機能方面<br />\nEg行山路過灣撞到山邊啲石，個轆有機會歪左，直接影響部車轉向同速度，隔離重會有個圖示部車有咩位損壞左（無事就白色，損壞左就紅色，分損壞程度變色） 如果真係壞左，每個圈完左可以番入維修區修理，修理完就繼續比賽咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry 199999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但真係想搵番，或者類似嘅game ,可能都係情意結黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外想集思廣益下有無以前機場管理員嘅ps4 game <br />\n另一個情意結，那些年唔捨得玩住嘅那霸機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTplink不了 ，咩router 好用，買黎連機"},{"pid":"4a259c953c0f4cfa4a812b0630cb0c11c989786b","tid":195943,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:38:41.000Z","msg":"鍾意玩探索同埋駕駛既話<br />\n可以試下no man sky"},{"pid":"00180a1e4ea6e9776ae1391d97f6186bf31256c8","tid":195943,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:16:11.000Z","msg":"鍾意射擊可以玩 divison"},{"pid":"a1a18c597228c01cd4437fe1d89f2051c4a48279","tid":195943,"uid":64615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意玩探索同埋駕駛既話<br />\n可以試下no man sky</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇左個trailer , no man sky 不了 <br />\n多謝你答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmo